import { Route, Routes } from "react-router-dom"
import { Colordes } from "./colordes"
import { Txtdes } from "./txtdes"

export const Routing=()=>
{
    return<>
    <Routes>
        <Route path="co" element={<Colordes></Colordes>} ></Route>
        <Route path="txt" element={<Txtdes></Txtdes>} ></Route>
    </Routes>
    </>
}
